217
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:31,900
   

218
00:24:34,900 --> 00:24:40,607
   

219
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,885
Mr. Shen.

220
00:24:49,885 --> 00:24:51,745
Pass me the bowl.

221
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,420
Is it enough for you?

222
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:09,680
Yes, sure.

223
00:25:14,860 --> 00:25:20,000
Four relics of ill omen subdued, yet five stars lit.

224
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:22,320
Where's the fifth one?

