232
00:26:21,900 --> 00:26:23,680
- Hello? 
 -  Hey, Luo Ren. 

233
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:25,440
 I've wrapped things up here. 

234
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:27,286
 I'll be heading back to Lixi tomorrow. 

235
00:26:27,286 --> 00:26:29,000
I was just about to call you.

236
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:31,640
Mu Dai and the others seem to have gone missing.

237
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:32,880
 What happened? 

238
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:36,000
 From the group chat, I learned she and Thirteen-Thousand went to Cao Village. 

239
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:40,160
Right. Chubby went missing, so they went to investigate.

240
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:43,151
But now they've lost contact too.

241
00:26:43,151 --> 00:26:44,940
It's been over 10 hours.

242
00:26:44,940 --> 00:26:47,280
- I'm on my way to Cao Village now. 
 -  I'll go with you. 

243
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:48,960
 I'll arrive later than you. 

244
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:51,080
It's all right. It'd be better you stay at the base.

245
00:26:51,080 --> 00:26:53,040
If I also go missing, at least there's a backup.

246
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:55,300
 Hey. Don't jinx it. 

247
00:26:55,300 --> 00:26:57,840
 Send me the location of Cao Village. 

248
00:26:57,840 --> 00:26:58,920
I'll enter the mountains later.

249
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:00,080
I brought a satellite phone with me.

250
00:27:00,080 --> 00:27:02,720
If I lose contact, you know what to do.

251
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:26,120
Qing Shan, let's set up two more tables before the stage.

252
00:28:26,120 --> 00:28:27,120
Like this.

253
00:28:27,120 --> 00:28:29,800
What do you think?

254
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:32,060
Oh, I see.

255
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,640
This rain won't let up.

256
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:41,040
What if it doesn't stop by then?

257
00:28:41,040 --> 00:28:45,520
Auntie, rain on the wedding day is considered auspicious.

258
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:47,420
We shouldn't complain.

259
00:28:47,420 --> 00:28:49,220
All right.

260
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:07,780
Excuse me, is Cao Qing Shan home?

261
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:13,240
Yes. How can I help you?

262
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:18,080
Are you Cao Qing Shan?

263
00:29:18,080 --> 00:29:20,440
That's right.

264
00:29:21,600 --> 00:29:22,940
I'm looking for my friends.

265
00:29:22,940 --> 00:29:25,281
They arrived yesterday. A man and a woman.

266
00:29:25,281 --> 00:29:27,086
Qing Shan, I'll leave you to it.

267
00:29:27,086 --> 00:29:28,627
I'll double-check it.

268
00:29:28,627 --> 00:29:30,008
Thanks, Auntie.

269
00:29:30,008 --> 00:29:32,078
No worries.

270
00:29:32,078 --> 00:29:34,318
Let's talk over here.

271
00:29:38,600 --> 00:29:42,500
They're from Yan City and are here to meet my cousin Cao Yan Hua.

272
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:45,280
- Right? 
 - Yes.

273
00:29:45,280 --> 00:29:46,720
They left early this morning.

274
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:49,680
- Left? 
 - Yes, they're gone.

275
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:57,280
They did mention they wouldn't stay long.

276
00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:59,770
But I didn't expect them to leave so soon.

277
00:29:59,770 --> 00:30:01,200
They only checked in yesterday.

278
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:04,900
But when I came by this morning, they had already gone.

279
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:18,200
And you are...

280
00:30:22,751 --> 00:30:24,792
I'm Luo, also a friend of Cao Yan Hua's.

281
00:30:24,792 --> 00:30:28,160
I was supposed to arrive yesterday but got delayed.

282
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:30,660
Thought they'd still be waiting for me.

283
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:32,480
But who knows?

284
00:30:35,180 --> 00:30:37,980
This is a big room.

285
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:44,680
My place may be simple, but the surroundings are pleasant.

286
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:46,900
Indeed.

287
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:50,900
Brother Luo, this rain shows no sign of stopping.

288
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:52,320
Here's an idea.

289
00:30:52,320 --> 00:30:54,920
Why don't you stay here tonight?

290
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:58,360
Well, my cousin's friend is my friend.

291
00:30:58,940 --> 00:31:01,100
That's very kind of you to offer.

292
00:31:01,100 --> 00:31:03,460
- Sorry for the trouble. 
 - No worries.

293
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:08,200
Speaking of which,

294
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:11,480
were you all invited by my cousin as wedding guests?

295
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:15,020
Why hasn't he shown up yet?

296
00:31:15,020 --> 00:31:18,560
Maybe he's saving the surprise for the wedding.

297
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:20,300
Could be.

298
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:22,480
Makes sense.

299
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:27,060
With so many people at the wedding, my uncle wouldn't dare punish him.

300
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:34,940
Did my two friends talk with anyone during their stay?

301
00:31:34,940 --> 00:31:37,400
They did. With Sister Jin Hua.

302
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:38,920
Sister Jin Hua?

303
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,340
Cao Jin Hua.

304
00:31:40,340 --> 00:31:42,740
They spoke for quite a while.

305
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:47,480
Well, anyone else?

306
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:49,640
Also...

307
00:31:50,983 --> 00:31:55,280
The girl met Ya Feng.

308
00:31:55,280 --> 00:32:01,280
My aunt told me she gave Ya Feng a red envelope and left.

309
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:03,450
Sorry.

310
00:32:03,450 --> 00:32:07,300
Ya Feng is my fiancée.

311
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:09,540
Excuse me, is Cao Jin Hua home?

312
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:15,860
Looking for you?

313
00:33:23,180 --> 00:33:24,980
Is Cao Jin Hua here?

314
00:33:26,120 --> 00:33:28,380
You're Cao Jin Hua?

315
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:33,600
Could we speak in private?

316
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:37,505
Just give me a moment. I'll be right there.

317
00:33:37,505 --> 00:33:39,066
Hold on. Just a second.

318
00:33:39,066 --> 00:33:40,946
I'll be right back!

319
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,770
Come in.

320
00:33:49,340 --> 00:33:50,940
Come on in.

321
00:33:56,180 --> 00:33:59,244
This is my place. Make yourself comfortable.

322
00:33:59,244 --> 00:34:00,724
Have a seat.

323
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:08,500
So, what brought you here?

324
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:13,073
Here's the thing. Two days ago, you spoke with two people at Qing Shan's place.

325
00:34:13,073 --> 00:34:15,820
- A man and a woman. 
 - That's right.

326
00:34:15,820 --> 00:34:18,205
And you are?

327
00:34:18,205 --> 00:34:20,880
Oh, I get it. You must be Henry, right?

328
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:23,280
- Henry? 
 - Yes, their brother.

329
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,400
 Henry Luo. 

330
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:26,181
 We share the same brother. 

331
00:34:26,181 --> 00:34:27,682
 Her brother is my brother. 

332
00:34:27,682 --> 00:34:29,602
 My brother will pay. 

333
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,640
I heard you guys talk for a long time.

334
00:34:31,640 --> 00:34:33,540
- About what? 
 - Insurance.

335
00:34:33,540 --> 00:34:36,320
- Insurance? 
 - Yes, insurance.

336
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:40,840
The risks lurking everywhere are like storms battering our lives.

337
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:42,000
And what is insurance?

338
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:45,200
It's the umbrella over your head when disaster strikes.

339
00:34:45,200 --> 00:34:46,860
It shelters you from wind and rain,

340
00:34:46,860 --> 00:34:49,380
- from the scorching sun— 
 - Risks are everywhere.

341
00:34:50,160 --> 00:34:52,440
Did you buy insurance for yourself?

342
00:34:53,940 --> 00:34:57,760
I... Well, I did.

343
00:34:57,760 --> 00:35:01,860
How can clients trust me if I don't even buy it myself?

344
00:35:03,100 --> 00:35:04,280
I really did.

345
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:09,400
Here. I'll show you my business promotion materials.

346
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,900
Take a look.

347
00:35:16,300 --> 00:35:21,260
Well, you're handsome, but way too impulsive.

348
00:35:21,260 --> 00:35:22,640
So, you only talked about insurance?

349
00:35:22,640 --> 00:35:23,840
Yes, really.

350
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:25,920
Ask me anything, and I'll tell you.

351
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:30,500
Oh, right, this phone has a number.

352
00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:32,020
It was left by the girl.

353
00:35:32,020 --> 00:35:34,140
She said Henry kept all her money, 
    

354
00:35:34,140 --> 00:35:36,680
and I should talk to Henry about buying insurance.

355
00:35:36,680 --> 00:35:38,540
See for yourself.

356
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:46,560
Sorry. I may have misunderstood something.

357
00:35:46,560 --> 00:35:48,440
No, no misunderstanding.

358
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:51,100
- Wait... 
 - Where did they go afterward?

359
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:54,720
Mrs. Cao said she took the girl to meet the bride.

360
00:35:54,720 --> 00:35:57,440
I wanted to talk to them about their needs,

361
00:35:57,440 --> 00:36:00,000
but Qing Shan said they left early.

362
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:07,500
Ya Feng, I'm heading out.

363
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,505
Are you Ya Feng?

364
00:36:34,505 --> 00:36:36,565
Who are you?

365
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:39,000
I'm looking for some people.

366
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:41,120
First, a chubby guy named Cao Yan Hua.

367
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:42,700
He's Qing Shan's cousin.

368
00:36:42,700 --> 00:36:45,560
Then a young lady. She gave you a red envelope.

369
00:36:45,560 --> 00:36:47,200
Remember?

370
00:36:52,260 --> 00:36:55,280
Just go. Stop looking for them.

371
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:56,720
Or it'll be too late.

372
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:59,180
You know where they are, don't you?

373
00:37:00,900 --> 00:37:03,420
Ya Feng, tell me.

374
00:37:04,660 --> 00:37:07,400
- Please leave. 
 - Ya Feng, you have to tell me!

375
00:37:47,820 --> 00:37:52,120
If they find out I tell you this, they'll kill me.

376
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:56,040
Trust me. They won't know.

377
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:05,100
That mountain is quite tall,

378
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:07,540
with a flat peak, as if it were sliced off.

379
00:38:07,540 --> 00:38:09,440
Easy to spot.

380
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:12,000
The cave's halfway up the mountain.

381
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,640
Remember, I was never here.

